00:00:16.914 --> 00:00:19.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wish we didn't have to.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's like a sculpture</c.bg_transparent>

8
00:00:19.314 --> 00:00:21.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>a monument to your year as a bachelor.</c.bg_transparent>

9
00:00:21.353 --> 00:00:22.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, I suppose it is.</c.bg_transparent>

10
00:00:22.872 --> 00:00:24.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are we to dismantle this piece of art?</c.bg_transparent>

11
00:00:25.723 --> 00:00:25.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

12
00:00:26.751 --> 00:00:28.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But if we don't, Keiko'll dismantle me.</c.bg_transparent>

13
00:00:46.905 --> 00:00:48.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy.</c.bg_transparent>

14
00:00:48.704 --> 00:00:49.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hi, sweetie.</c.bg_transparent>

15
00:00:50.224 --> 00:00:51.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>

16
00:00:54.943 --> 00:00:55.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hi.</c.bg_transparent>

17
00:01:03.420 --> 00:01:05.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The one good thing about going away</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is coming home.</c.bg_transparent>

18
00:01:06.459 --> 00:01:08.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never want to be apart like that again.</c.bg_transparent>

19
00:01:08.898 --> 00:01:12.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy, Daddy! I have a little brother</c.bg_transparent>

20
00:01:12.817 --> 00:01:15.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really? Is that him?</c.bg_transparent>

21
00:01:16.256 --> 00:01:17.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. He's in there.</c.bg_transparent>

22
00:01:19.735 --> 00:01:20.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

23
00:01:23.294 --> 00:01:24.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A baby?</c.bg_transparent>

24
00:01:25.573 --> 00:01:29.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah. I--I thought you'd be happy.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, we talked about it</c.bg_transparent>

25
00:01:29.812 --> 00:01:31.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and decided we'd start trying.</c.bg_transparent>

26
00:01:31.932 --> 00:01:35.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I know.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We--We--Well, but your last visit,</c.bg_transparent>

27
00:01:35.930 --> 00:01:37.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you were only here the one night, and...</c.bg_transparent>

28
00:01:38.329 --> 00:01:40.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought it'd take a couple of nights.</c.bg_transparent>

29
00:01:40.809 --> 00:01:44.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To be honest... a lot more nights.</c.bg_transparent>

30
00:01:45.248 --> 00:01:47.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess we just got lucky this time.</c.bg_transparent>

31
00:01:49.527 --> 00:01:50.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess so.</c.bg_transparent>

32
00:01:58.839 --> 00:02:00.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Vedek Porta.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Nerys.</c.bg_transparent>

33
00:02:00.883 --> 00:02:06.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, this is where you are</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when you're not at the Temple.</c.bg_transparent>

34
00:02:08.480 --> 00:02:09.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very impressive.</c.bg_transparent>

35
00:02:10.405 --> 00:02:11.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Haven't you ever been to Ops?</c.bg_transparent>

36
00:02:11.639 --> 00:02:16.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What business would an old monk have here,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>except maybe helping a young couple</c.bg_transparent>

37
00:02:16.238 --> 00:02:17.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to meet the Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

38
00:02:19.777 --> 00:02:20.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure this is a good time?</c.bg_transparent>

39
00:02:21.157 --> 00:02:22.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think he'll be able to fit you in.</c.bg_transparent>

40
00:02:22.837 --> 00:02:24.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you so much for doing this, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

41
00:02:24.795 --> 00:02:26.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I'm glad to.</c.bg_transparent>

42
00:02:28.875 --> 00:02:30.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They can take the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Rubicon.</i></c.bg_transparent>

43
00:02:30.354 --> 00:02:31.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

44
00:02:31.673 --> 00:02:33.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in.</c.bg_transparent>

45
00:02:34.193 --> 00:02:35.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vedek Porta's here</c.bg_transparent>

46
00:02:35.232 --> 00:02:36.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>with the young couple</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that just got married.</c.bg_transparent>

47
00:02:37.232 --> 00:02:38.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're hoping</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get the Emissary's blessing.</c.bg_transparent>

48
00:02:40.715 --> 00:02:40.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bring them in.</c.bg_transparent>

49
00:02:44.230 --> 00:02:46.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You remember the words?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The marriage blessing?</c.bg_transparent>

50
00:02:46.150 --> 00:02:47.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Mm-hmm.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I think so.</c.bg_transparent>

51
00:02:50.348 --> 00:02:53.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Emissary, we're very grateful to you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for seeing us.</c.bg_transparent>

52
00:02:53.787 --> 00:02:54.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

53
00:02:55.307 --> 00:02:56.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, if you'll just join hands...</c.bg_transparent>

54
00:03:00.305 --> 00:03:03.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Zhia'kala, tar'eh anu suur...</i></c.bg_transparent>

55
00:03:04.224 --> 00:03:06.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>te'von, aka'lu rez... ka'vor</i></c.bg_transparent>

56
00:03:07.183 --> 00:03:08.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>mat'ana kel.</i></c.bg_transparent>

57
00:03:09.623 --> 00:03:10.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

58
00:03:10.142 --> 00:03:11.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you very much.</c.bg_transparent>

59
00:03:16.420 --> 00:03:19.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your accent is getting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>much better, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

60
00:03:19.379 --> 00:03:20.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm glad to hear it.</c.bg_transparent>

61
00:03:23.818 --> 00:03:25.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighing )</c.bg_transparent>

62
00:03:26.179 --> 00:03:28.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It isn't that bad, is it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>being the Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

63
00:03:30.256 --> 00:03:32.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A few ceremonies, an occasional blessing.</c.bg_transparent>

64
00:03:33.455 --> 00:03:34.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't say it was that bad.</c.bg_transparent>

65
00:03:34.695 --> 00:03:37.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's just hard getting used</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to being a religious icon.</c.bg_transparent>

66
00:03:38.293 --> 00:03:40.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-DAX: Really?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I think I'd like it.</c.bg_transparent>

67
00:03:40.973 --> 00:03:42.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Kira to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

68
00:03:42.732 --> 00:03:44.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-You'd better get out here.</i></c.bg_transparent>

69
00:03:44.972 --> 00:03:46.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>There's something</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>coming through the wormhole.</i></c.bg_transparent>

70
00:03:59.887 --> 00:04:00.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A lightship.</c.bg_transparent>

71
00:04:00.767 --> 00:04:01.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: I don't know where it came from.</c.bg_transparent>

72
00:04:01.886 --> 00:04:04.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to remote sensors,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it never entered the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

73
00:04:04.325 --> 00:04:06.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>From these readings, I'd say that ship's</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about 300 years old.</c.bg_transparent>

74
00:04:06.805 --> 00:04:07.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Life signs?</c.bg_transparent>

75
00:04:08.285 --> 00:04:09.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's someone on board,</c.bg_transparent>

76
00:04:09.645 --> 00:04:11.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-a Bajoran.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Try hailing them.</c.bg_transparent>

77
00:04:12.524 --> 00:04:13.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: No response.</c.bg_transparent>

78
00:04:14.163 --> 00:04:16.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Whoever's in there could be injured.</c.bg_transparent>

79
00:04:17.202 --> 00:04:19.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tractor the ship into transporter range</c.bg_transparent>

80
00:04:19.820 --> 00:04:21.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and beam the passenger</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>directly into the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

81
00:04:25.960 --> 00:04:27.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

82
00:04:31.158 --> 00:04:32.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's a little disoriented.</c.bg_transparent>

83
00:04:35.117 --> 00:04:37.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Captain Benjamin Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

84
00:04:37.635 --> 00:04:40.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're aboard a Federation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>space station near Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

85
00:04:40.595 --> 00:04:42.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Kira Nerys, my First Officer.</c.bg_transparent>

86
00:04:45.714 --> 00:04:46.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are you?</c.bg_transparent>

87
00:04:48.713 --> 00:04:49.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

88
00:06:48.476 --> 00:06:52.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was headed back to Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>My lightship was caught in an ion storm.</c.bg_transparent>

89
00:06:53.715 --> 00:06:55.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It nearly tore it apart.</c.bg_transparent>

90
00:06:56.635 --> 00:07:00.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>A girder came loose from the bulkhead</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and impaled me through the shoulder, here.</c.bg_transparent>

91
00:07:00.912 --> 00:07:04.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember thinking I was going to die</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>alone in space</c.bg_transparent>

92
00:07:04.952 --> 00:07:08.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>when a strange opening</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>appeared in the sky.</c.bg_transparent>

93
00:07:08.590 --> 00:07:13.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>AKOREM: I was terrified at first,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and then, I realized what was happening.</c.bg_transparent>

94
00:07:15.509 --> 00:07:19.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets were opening the gates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Celestial Temple</c.bg_transparent>

95
00:07:20.747 --> 00:07:22.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>and drawing me to them.</c.bg_transparent>

96
00:07:23.306 --> 00:07:24.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened then?</c.bg_transparent>

97
00:07:24.785 --> 00:07:26.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>AKOREM: It's difficult to describe.</c.bg_transparent>

98
00:07:26.666 --> 00:07:32.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They took the form of people that I know,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my grandfather, my brother,</c.bg_transparent>

99
00:07:32.863 --> 00:07:34.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>AKOREM: so they could communicate with me.</c.bg_transparent>

100
00:07:35.583 --> 00:07:38.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You spoke to them?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I didn't have to.</c.bg_transparent>

101
00:07:38.221 --> 00:07:41.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could sense</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their understanding, their grace.</c.bg_transparent>

102
00:07:43.580 --> 00:07:46.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never felt such bliss.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And then they healed me.</c.bg_transparent>

103
00:07:47.299 --> 00:07:51.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>A light washed over me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and then my wound was gone.</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:07:52.578 --> 00:07:56.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave me back my life. I felt reborn.</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:07:56.896 --> 00:07:58.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>When exactly did you leave Bajor?</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:07:59.976 --> 00:08:02.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, it couldn't have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>been more than a few days ago.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:08:02.975 --> 00:08:03.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was the year?</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:08:04.614 --> 00:08:05.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>9174.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:09.932 --> 00:08:11.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was over 200 years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:13.691 --> 00:08:14.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>200 years?</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:19.249 --> 00:08:20.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>My wife...</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:21.129 --> 00:08:23.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>My parents... they're gone.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:25.568 --> 00:08:27.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: If you give us your name,</c.bg_transparent>

