00:08:27.407 --> 00:08:29.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>maybe we can contact your descendants.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:29.846 --> 00:08:32.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
