125
00:09:06.595 --> 00:09:09.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps, that's part</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Prophets' plan for me.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:10.754 --> 00:09:11.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their plan?</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:12.743 --> 00:09:14.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not clear to me yet</c.bg_transparent>
