<c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarra?</i></c.bg_transparent>

135
00:09:37.866 --> 00:09:39.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor used to have a strict caste system.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:09:39.945 --> 00:09:42.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
