137
00:09:44.984 --> 00:09:47.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You no longer follow your </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras?</i></c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:47.383 --> 00:09:49.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When the Cardassians occupied Bajor,</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:49.223 --> 00:09:52.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we gave up the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras,</i></c.bg_transparent>
