140
00:09:53.141 --> 00:09:54.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We all became soldiers.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:55.340 --> 00:09:57.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Cardassians occupied Bajor?</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:58.100 --> 00:09:58.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For over 50 years.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:02.659 --> 00:10:04.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems you're right, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:10:04.418 --> 00:10:07.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A great deal has happened</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since I've been gone.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:15.255 --> 00:10:17.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you look at the prophecies</c.bg_transparent>
