<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:10:34.289 --> 00:10:35.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They didn't give me back my life.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:10:37.448 --> 00:10:40.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not literally, but they did help you</c.bg_transparent>
