173
00:11:30.192 --> 00:11:31.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How does it feel?</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:11:31.831 --> 00:11:34.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It feels, uh... good.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:11:35.311 --> 00:11:36.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No more ceremonies to attend.</c.bg_transparent>

176
