180
00:11:50.307 --> 00:11:52.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel like I'm on vacation.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:59.863 --> 00:12:00.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
