<c.bg_transparent>I thought your females carried your young.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:12:19.577 --> 00:12:22.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My wife. My wife is having the baby.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:12:23.497 --> 00:12:24.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Congratulations.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:12:25.496 --> 00:12:28.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember when my nephew Nog was a baby.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:12:28.495 --> 00:12:30.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cutest thing you ever saw.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:12:31.733 --> 00:12:32.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
