196
00:12:36.132 --> 00:12:38.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I used to love reading to him.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:38.891 --> 00:12:43.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, "See Brak acquire.</c.bg_transparent>
