<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:13:14.920 --> 00:13:16.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seven months.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:13:16.961 --> 00:13:17.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:13:18.919 --> 00:13:21.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Worf delivered Molly, you know.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Really?</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:13:21.959 --> 00:13:23.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> was damaged.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:13:23.399 --> 00:13:25.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keiko and he were trapped</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>together when her time came.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:13:26.278 --> 00:13:29.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, well, I'll, uh, be sure and call you</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:13:29.157 --> 00:13:30.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when she's ready to deliver.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You can lend a hand.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:13:31.356 --> 00:13:32.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seven months?</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:13:33.755 --> 00:13:36.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unfortunately, I will be away</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the station at that time.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:13:36.914 --> 00:13:38.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:13:38.913 --> 00:13:39.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Far away.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:13:41.593 --> 00:13:43.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Visiting my parents... On Earth.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:13:46.152 --> 00:13:47.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:13:47.351 --> 00:13:50.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:13:50.670 --> 00:13:53.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know who's more anxious</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about this baby, you or Worf.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:13:56.228 --> 00:13:58.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The thing is, Julian,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>now that Molly's a little older,</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:13:58.988 --> 00:14:01.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was hoping to be able to spend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>some time with Keiko again.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:14:02.587 --> 00:14:07.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought we could... I don't know...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>go out at night. Don't get me wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:14:07.785 --> 00:14:09.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know once I hold my little baby</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in my arms,</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:14:09.784 --> 00:14:12.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll be the happiest man</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the world, but...</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:14:12.304 --> 00:14:14.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wasn't expecting it to happen so soon.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:14:18.222 --> 00:14:20.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How about a game of darts?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Don't you have to go home?</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:14:21.821 --> 00:14:22.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:14:38.176 --> 00:14:40.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, come to see Akorem speak?</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:14:40.695 --> 00:14:43.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Emissary's first public appearance?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't miss it.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:14:43.534 --> 00:14:45.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm surprised to hear you call him that.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:14:45.693 --> 00:14:46.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:14:46.894 --> 00:14:50.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Akorem Laan was... is a great man.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:14:50.532 --> 00:14:51.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's been with the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for over 200 years,</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:14:52.119 --> 00:14:53.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and now they sent him back to us.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:14:53.612 --> 00:14:57.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, but two days ago, you believed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Captain Sisko was the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:14:57.810 --> 00:14:59.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, he made it clear,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he wants to step aside.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:15:00.330 --> 00:15:04.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Does that mean he never really</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was the Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:15:04.728 --> 00:15:05.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:15:06.527 --> 00:15:08.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But they can't both be.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:15:10.207 --> 00:15:12.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want from me, Odo?</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:15:13.646 --> 00:15:15.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive me, Major.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't mean to be difficult,</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:15:15.444 --> 00:15:17.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but your faith seems to have led you</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:15:17.244 --> 00:15:21.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-to something of a contradiction.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't see it as a contradiction.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:15:22.882 --> 00:15:24.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:15:25.922 --> 00:15:27.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's the thing about faith,</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:15:28.401 --> 00:15:30.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>if you don't have it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you can't understand it,</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:15:30.320 --> 00:15:33.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and if you do,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no explanation is necessary.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:15:35.519 --> 00:15:37.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( applause )</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:15:48.395 --> 00:15:51.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ever since the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>returned me to my people,</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:15:51.954 --> 00:15:55.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've asked myself the same questions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>over and over again.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:15:55.993 --> 00:15:58.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why did they keep me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with them for so long?</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:15:59.751 --> 00:16:02.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why did they return me to my people now?</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:16:03.708 --> 00:16:04.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I now know the answers.</i></c.bg_transparent>

260
00:16:04.670 --> 00:16:08.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Bajor suffered a great wound</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>while I was with the Prophets,</i></c.bg_transparent>

261
00:16:09.295 --> 00:16:10.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>the Cardassian Occupation.</i></c.bg_transparent>

262
00:16:11.308 --> 00:16:13.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The Bajor that I've returned</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to has lost its way.</i></c.bg_transparent>

263
00:16:14.667 --> 00:16:17.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>People no longer follow the path</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>the Prophets have laid out for them.</i></c.bg_transparent>

264
00:16:18.785 --> 00:16:20.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>They no longer follow their </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>D'jarras.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:16:21.465 --> 00:16:25.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Artists have become soldiers.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Priests have become merchants.</i></c.bg_transparent>

266
00:16:25.704 --> 00:16:31.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Farmers have become politicians.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We must heal the wounds of the occupation.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:16:31.302 --> 00:16:34.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We must return to our </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras.</i></c.bg_transparent>

268
00:16:35.221 --> 00:16:38.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We must reclaim what we were</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and follow the path</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:16:38.500 --> 00:16:40.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets have laid out for us.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:16:40.899 --> 00:16:44.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is their will that farmers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>return to their land,</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:16:44.378 --> 00:16:47.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>painters to their canvasses,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>priests to their temples.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:16:48.377 --> 00:16:52.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we do this, if we follow our </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras,</i></c.bg_transparent>

273
00:16:52.655 --> 00:16:54.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>then Bajor will flourish again</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:16:54.615 --> 00:16:57.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and become the green and peaceful</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>land I remember.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:16:57.854 --> 00:17:01.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It will be as if the occupation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>never happened.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:17:02.293 --> 00:17:07.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>By returning to our </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we will have erased it forever.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:17:07.411 --> 00:17:08.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( applause )</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:17:25.886 --> 00:17:28.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted to talk to you before</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you left for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:17:28.724 --> 00:17:29.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:17:30.404 --> 00:17:32.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was surprised by your speech.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:17:32.683 --> 00:17:34.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had no idea you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were going to advocate change</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:17:34.803 --> 00:17:36.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on such a massive scale.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:17:38.402 --> 00:17:39.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's what the Prophets want for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:17:40.561 --> 00:17:41.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's why they sent me.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:17:41.601 --> 00:17:42.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure of that?</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:17:43.201 --> 00:17:44.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Absolutely.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:17:44.440 --> 00:17:46.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Emissary knows that what</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he's proposing</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:17:46.679 --> 00:17:48.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>will be difficult for some people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to accept.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:17:49.158 --> 00:17:51.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He doesn't expect things</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to change overnight.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:17:52.380 --> 00:17:54.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you're not going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to ask First Minister Shakaar</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:17:54.877 --> 00:17:56.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to step down and go back to farming?</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:17:56.956 --> 00:17:58.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, of course not.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:17:58.476 --> 00:18:00.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But frankly, by the next election,</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:18:00.275 --> 00:18:02.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I doubt very many people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be left on Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:18:02.594 --> 00:18:04.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>who would elect a farmer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to political office.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:18:04.914 --> 00:18:07.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We hope that, eventually,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the people will support</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:18:07.993 --> 00:18:10.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>enforcement of the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by legal sanction.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:18:11.751 --> 00:18:13.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, if someone defies their caste?</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:18:14.318 --> 00:18:18.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Society will have appropriate remedies</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at its disposal, such as deportation.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:18:21.297 --> 00:18:23.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You realize that caste-based</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>discrimination</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:18:23.828 --> 00:18:29.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>goes against the Federation Charter.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If Bajor returns to the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarra </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>system,</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:18:29.547 --> 00:18:33.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have no doubt that its petition</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to join the Federation will be rejected.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:18:34.145 --> 00:18:36.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kai Winn and I have already discussed it.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:18:36.904 --> 00:18:38.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're willing to make that sacrifice</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:18:38.343 --> 00:18:40.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>in order to follow the will</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:18:42.629 --> 00:18:44.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had a feeling Winn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would see it that way.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:18:45.582 --> 00:18:48.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, the Emissary's transport</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>leaves shortly.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:18:52.739 --> 00:18:58.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a Starfleet officer, I am bound by oath</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>not to interfere with Bajoran affairs,</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:18:58.657 --> 00:19:02.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but... as a friend to Bajor,</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:19:03.417 --> 00:19:05.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to say</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>giving up Federation membership</c.bg_transparent>

311
