<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:26:45.998 --> 00:26:47.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can Daddy color, too?</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:26:47.198 --> 00:26:48.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm coloring.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:27:13.989 --> 00:27:17.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The four-shift rotation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>also seems to be improving performance.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:27:17.268 --> 00:27:18.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Less mistakes due to fatigue.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:27:19.428 --> 00:27:22.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fine. Let's make the change permanent.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Anything else?</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:27:25.386 --> 00:27:27.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was wondering if, in the next few days</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:27:27.705 --> 00:27:30.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you would have the time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to meet with Major Jatarn.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:27:31.648 --> 00:27:31.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sure.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:27:34.623 --> 00:27:35.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is something wrong, sir?</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:27:37.263 --> 00:27:38.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:27:39.102 --> 00:27:42.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just received a communiqué</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from Starfleet Command</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:27:42.141 --> 00:27:44.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>responding to my report</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the Bajoran situation.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:27:45.140 --> 00:27:45.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That bad?</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:27:46.999 --> 00:27:47.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not yet,</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:27:47.819 --> 00:27:49.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I can read between the lines.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:27:52.377 --> 00:27:56.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was sent here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to help bring Bajor into the Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:27:56.816 --> 00:27:59.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't look like much</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of a possibility anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:27:59.296 --> 00:28:00.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As far as Starfleet is concerned,</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:28:01.555 --> 00:28:02.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have failed my mission.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:28:03.494 --> 00:28:06.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not fair. It's not your fault.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:28:07.174 --> 00:28:08.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is from where they're sitting.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:28:09.893 --> 00:28:13.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The irony is, Starfleet was always trying</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:28:13.371 --> 00:28:16.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to get me to distance myself</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from this Emissary business.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:28:16.131 --> 00:28:17.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And now that I have...</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:28:22.209 --> 00:28:24.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe I could talk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to First Minister Shakaar</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:28:24.328 --> 00:28:26.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>about sending Starfleet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a communiqué explai--</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:28:26.448 --> 00:28:28.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Thanks.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It--it'll blow over.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:28:29.846 --> 00:28:31.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not that.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:28:32.806 --> 00:28:34.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess I'm just feeling...</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:28:36.855 --> 00:28:36.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did fail.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:28:38.644 --> 00:28:39.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir...</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:28:39.804 --> 00:28:44.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anyway, why did you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>want me to meet Jatarn?</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:28:45.322 --> 00:28:46.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:28:47.721 --> 00:28:49.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can talk about that another time.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:28:49.521 --> 00:28:50.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it, Major?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:28:52.760 --> 00:28:54.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think he'd make an excellent</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>First Officer.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:28:56.838 --> 00:28:58.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As soon as you can find someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to take my post,</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:28:58.758 --> 00:29:00.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to resign my commission.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:29:01.517 --> 00:29:02.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:29:02.397 --> 00:29:04.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To follow your...</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> D'jarra.</i></c.bg_transparent>

457
00:29:06.476 --> 00:29:08.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm planning to move back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Dahkur Province.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:29:08.595 --> 00:29:10.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are a lot of artists</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who live in the capital,</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:29:11.743 --> 00:29:13.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I have a friend there who's willing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to apprentice me.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:29:15.713 --> 00:29:16.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:29:18.352 --> 00:29:21.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last thing I want to do is to add</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your problems.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:29:24.710 --> 00:29:26.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is something I have to do.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:29:30.509 --> 00:29:32.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sniffles )</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:29:33.987 --> 00:29:35.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If, um...</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:29:36.466 --> 00:29:38.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't hit it off</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Major Jatarn, um,</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:29:38.666 --> 00:29:40.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can think of a few other people.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:29:40.705 --> 00:29:42.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It shouldn't be that hard to find someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to replace me.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:29:43.904 --> 00:29:47.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't doubt that I can find</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone to fill your post...</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:29:50.422 --> 00:29:51.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But to replace you?</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:29:58.980 --> 00:30:01.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens, closes )</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:30:08.177 --> 00:30:09.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, time.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:30:09.776 --> 00:30:12.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>1921 hours.</i></c.bg_transparent>

473
00:30:12.176 --> 00:30:13.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where's Dr. Bashir?</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:30:13.615 --> 00:30:15.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dr. Bashir is in Quark's bar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

475
00:30:22.372 --> 00:30:24.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm chasing a triple 17</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and a bull, Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:30:24.732 --> 00:30:26.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Got some catching up to do.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:30:26.211 --> 00:30:27.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief!</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:30:29.811 --> 00:30:30.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:30:35.409 --> 00:30:36.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:30:36.648 --> 00:30:37.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How have you been?</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:30:37.808 --> 00:30:39.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not bad. You?</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:30:39.208 --> 00:30:40.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you know, all right.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:30:41.487 --> 00:30:44.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was heading home.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Thought I'd stop in for a quick pint.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:30:48.126 --> 00:30:48.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:30:49.285 --> 00:30:50.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's been a while, eh?</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:30:50.445 --> 00:30:52.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ha. Seems like weeks.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:30:53.483 --> 00:30:54.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see you found someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to play darts with.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:30:55.321 --> 00:30:55.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:30:56.402 --> 00:30:58.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've set a board up in our quarters</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so Molly and I can play.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:30:59.282 --> 00:31:01.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, Morn's, um... he's pretty good.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:31:01.121 --> 00:31:02.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So's Molly.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:31:03.360 --> 00:31:04.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's not the same.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's not the same.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:31:09.118 --> 00:31:13.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, Molly's just a kid.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know, we've been playing with magnets.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:31:13.718 --> 00:31:16.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn couldn't hit a Yridian yak</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at five paces.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:31:18.356 --> 00:31:19.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were evenly matched.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:31:19.876 --> 00:31:21.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We had a good rivalry going on.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:31:21.115 --> 00:31:22.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, kept us sharp.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:31:22.395 --> 00:31:23.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:31:24.634 --> 00:31:25.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're late.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:31:27.393 --> 00:31:28.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:31:29.113 --> 00:31:31.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's Thursday, and I've got your usual</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>holosuite reserved.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:31:32.112 --> 00:31:33.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Didn't you cancel?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:31:33.232 --> 00:31:35.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, I was, um, hoping maybe...</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:31:36.471 --> 00:31:38.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, no, I--I--I got to get home.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:31:39.630 --> 00:31:42.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about you, Doctor?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The Battle of Britain awaits.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:31:42.549 --> 00:31:45.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you know my policy on cancellations,</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:31:45.748 --> 00:31:47.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>no refunds.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:31:47.427 --> 00:31:48.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:31:48.747 --> 00:31:52.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe Morn's better in the cockpit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of a spitfire than he is at darts.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:31:52.466 --> 00:31:53.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, it wouldn't be the same.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:31:54.346 --> 00:31:56.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um... You're right.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:31:57.905 --> 00:32:00.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn probably doesn't even know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>where England is.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:32:01.383 --> 00:32:02.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs )</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:32:04.623 --> 00:32:05.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see you.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:32:15.819 --> 00:32:16.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

516
00:32:17.578 --> 00:32:18.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:32:18.698 --> 00:32:21.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You'd better come down to the Promenade.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Someone's been killed.</i></c.bg_transparent>

518
00:32:25.256 --> 00:32:26.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What happened?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-We don't know yet.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:32:26.776 --> 00:32:29.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He fell from the second level.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>His neck was broken on impact.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:32:29.734 --> 00:32:32.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Did anyone see it happen?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I did.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:32:34.539 --> 00:32:35.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Was it an accident?</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:32:36.136 --> 00:32:37.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I pushed him.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:32:38.532 --> 00:32:42.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>His family name is Imutta.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Their </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarra </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>is unclean.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:32:43.971 --> 00:32:45.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They prepare the dead for burial.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:32:45.810 --> 00:32:49.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I asked him to set the proper example</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and resign from our order.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:32:50.208 --> 00:32:51.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He refused.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:32:51.328 --> 00:32:53.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You killed him because of his </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarra?</i></c.bg_transparent>

528
00:32:54.167 --> 00:32:58.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had to. If a Vedek can't do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what the Emissary has asked of us,</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:32:58.806 --> 00:33:00.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>how can we expect anyone else to?</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:33:01.405 --> 00:33:02.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get him out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:33:13.601 --> 00:33:15.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I regret what happened here today</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:33:15.161 --> 00:33:18.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>as much as you do,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but change is never easy.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:33:19.799 --> 00:33:21.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The road that the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have asked us to walk</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:33:21.400 --> 00:33:23.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>won't always be a smooth one.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:33:23.119 --> 00:33:25.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And forcing people to follow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras</i></c.bg_transparent>

536
00:33:25.558 --> 00:33:26.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>won't make it any smoother.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:33:27.357 --> 00:33:29.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened on the Promenade</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was just the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:33:30.157 --> 00:33:31.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Must I remind you, Captain?</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:33:32.276 --> 00:33:34.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm merely fulfilling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the will of the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:33:34.875 --> 00:33:36.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know that?</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:33:37.794 --> 00:33:39.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:33:39.834 --> 00:33:41.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And what you've done with the position</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:33:41.593 --> 00:33:43.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has made me wish I had never given it up.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:33:44.333 --> 00:33:46.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you did,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it was the right decision.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:33:47.552 --> 00:33:49.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You never truly accepted</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the role in the first place.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:33:52.949 --> 00:33:54.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm willing to accept it now.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:33:58.348 --> 00:33:59.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're challenging my claim.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:34:00.428 --> 00:34:01.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've left me no choice.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:34:04.346 --> 00:34:05.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we went to the people</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:34:06.346 --> 00:34:09.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and asked them to choose</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between us, it would be chaos.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:34:09.305 --> 00:34:11.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to divide Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any more than you do.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:34:12.384 --> 00:34:14.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wouldn't be divided for long</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:34:14.103 --> 00:34:16.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because in the end,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the people would choose me.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:34:16.583 --> 00:34:19.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My claim was foretold</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the ancient texts.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:34:20.623 --> 00:34:24.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was the first to find the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was the first to be with the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:34:25.540 --> 00:34:27.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave me back my life.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:34:27.340 --> 00:34:30.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're not going to settle</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this by arguing over ancient texts.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:34:31.218 --> 00:34:32.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then how?</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:34:32.658 --> 00:34:35.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's only one way to be sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>which one of us is the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:34:37.256 --> 00:34:40.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have to go to the wormhole</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and ask the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:35:00.849 --> 00:35:02.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Going to half thrusters.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:35:03.888 --> 00:35:05.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:35:08.775 --> 00:35:08.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now what?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:35:10.675 --> 00:35:10.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We wait.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:35:36.119 --> 00:35:39.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( thudding heartbeat )</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:35:39.278 --> 00:35:41.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:35:41.437 --> 00:35:43.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the one that was injured.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:35:43.756 --> 00:35:47.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, I was. And you gave me back my life,</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:35:47.475 --> 00:35:49.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>just as the texts foretold.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:35:49.515 --> 00:35:51.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you here?</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:35:51.434 --> 00:35:54.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To... prove to this nonbeliever</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:35:54.954 --> 00:35:58.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that you sent me to put Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back on the right path.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:35:59.511 --> 00:36:03.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, tell him you chose me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be the Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:36:03.871 --> 00:36:06.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell that him that I fulfilled</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the ancient prophecies,</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:36:07.629 --> 00:36:10.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that I was the first to find</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Celestial Temple.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:36:10.389 --> 00:36:14.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was the first to meet with you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He came to you centuries later.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:36:14.907 --> 00:36:15.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>First...</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:36:17.186 --> 00:36:17.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Later...</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:36:19.264 --> 00:36:21.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They have no meaning to us.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:36:22.254 --> 00:36:24.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: The Bajorans believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you are their Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:36:24.184 --> 00:36:26.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That you have chosen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one of us to be your Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:36:32.942 --> 00:36:35.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We... are of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:36:36.581 --> 00:36:37.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:36:42.579 --> 00:36:44.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are linear.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:36:44.299 --> 00:36:46.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It limits them.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:36:46.578 --> 00:36:48.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They do not understand.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:36:48.577 --> 00:36:50.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But we want to understand.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:36:51.256 --> 00:36:52.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's why we're here.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:36:53.136 --> 00:36:54.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You saved his life. Why?</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:36:55.136 --> 00:36:56.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was injured.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:36:57.694 --> 00:36:58.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We kept him with us.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:36:58.894 --> 00:37:01.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So that I would be spared the occupation.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:37:01.133 --> 00:37:03.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So that I could bring</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>back to Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:37:03.852 --> 00:37:05.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that true?</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:37:05.652 --> 00:37:07.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that what you want?</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:37:08.513 --> 00:37:12.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>are part of what the Sisko</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would call the past.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:37:12.810 --> 00:37:17.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Sisko taught us that for you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what was can never be again.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:37:17.368 --> 00:37:21.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> belong in the past,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why did you send me into the future?</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:37:25.865 --> 00:37:26.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:37:27.845 --> 00:37:29.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For me?</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:37:30.325 --> 00:37:32.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're saying that he's your Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:37:33.924 --> 00:37:35.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:37:38.722 --> 00:37:40.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I've been wrong...</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:37:41.181 --> 00:37:42.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>About everything.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:37:43.801 --> 00:37:46.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should have let me die.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:37:46.520 --> 00:37:47.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We still can.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:37:49.399 --> 00:37:50.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can return him</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:37:50.838 --> 00:37:52.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to the moment we found him.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:37:53.758 --> 00:37:55.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Allow him to die.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:37:55.437 --> 00:37:56.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:37:57.276 --> 00:37:59.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why not return him to his own time</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:37:59.996 --> 00:38:05.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>as he is now, uninjured,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so that he can get back safely to Bajor?</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:38:10.353 --> 00:38:13.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He would remember</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>nothing of what has happened.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:38:15.151 --> 00:38:18.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could be with my wife and family.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:38:23.109 --> 00:38:24.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm ready to go home.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:38:26.428 --> 00:38:27.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:38:28.788 --> 00:38:30.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why do you stay here?</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:38:30.387 --> 00:38:32.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because I still have questions.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:38:34.106 --> 00:38:36.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:38:36.945 --> 00:38:38.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What does that mean?</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:38:39.464 --> 00:38:42.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You... </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>are of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:39:10.214 --> 00:39:12.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, Molly really loves</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that book Jake gave her.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:39:12.574 --> 00:39:15.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She made me read it to her three times</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before she fell asleep.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:39:20.371 --> 00:39:21.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:39:21.971 --> 00:39:23.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to be working another few hours.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:39:24.112 --> 00:39:27.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Well, that's okay.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll, uh... I'll read.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:39:28.369 --> 00:39:29.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you want to go do something...</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:39:30.129 --> 00:39:32.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:39:37.287 --> 00:39:38.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:39:39.405 --> 00:39:45.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, I promised I wouldn't say anything,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it's about Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:39:46.564 --> 00:39:47.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about him?</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:39:48.603 --> 00:39:51.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I ran into him the other day,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and he seemed depressed.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:39:51.482 --> 00:39:54.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'd never admit it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he really misses you.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:39:54.561 --> 00:39:55.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Poor guy.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:39:56.201 --> 00:39:58.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No family to come home to every night.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:39:59.120 --> 00:40:01.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe you should go find him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know, cheer him up a little.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:40:03.319 --> 00:40:05.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Depressed, is he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Very.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:40:05.638 --> 00:40:06.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe I should go spend an hour with him.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:40:07.438 --> 00:40:08.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe two.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:40:14.795 --> 00:40:15.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a lucky man.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:40:20.914 --> 00:40:22.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keiko to Dr. Bashir.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:40:22.713 --> 00:40:23.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Go ahead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

643
00:40:24.112 --> 00:40:25.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Julian, it's about Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:40:25.792 --> 00:40:30.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I promised I wouldn't tell anyone,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>but he's been really depressed lately.</i></c.bg_transparent>

645
00:40:31.351 --> 00:40:32.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:40:38.629 --> 00:40:39.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to have this.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:40:39.788 --> 00:40:43.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's an original Kira Nerys.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It could be very valuable one day.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:40:44.666 --> 00:40:46.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hear she didn't make many.</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:40:46.506 --> 00:40:47.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:40:50.584 --> 00:40:52.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought your speech</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>went very well yesterday.</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:40:53.248 --> 00:40:54.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was the right thing to do.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:40:55.143 --> 00:40:57.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted everyone to know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what happened to Akorem</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:40:57.742 --> 00:41:01.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and that the Prophets said nothing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about returning to the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>D'jarras.</i></c.bg_transparent>

654
00:41:02.217 --> 00:41:03.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just about everyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was relieved to hear it.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:41:04.207 --> 00:41:06.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's your own fault.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I can't believe you didn't cover me.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:41:06.260 --> 00:41:08.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How was I to know you were going to insult</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the King of Leinster?</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:41:08.699 --> 00:41:10.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Ah!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-In his own keep!</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:41:10.139 --> 00:41:11.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:41:11.738 --> 00:41:15.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just reading one of Akorem's poems,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>The Call of the Prophets.</i></c.bg_transparent>

660
00:41:15.417 --> 00:41:16.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that's one of my favorites.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:41:17.257 --> 00:41:18.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a shame he never finished it.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:41:19.256 --> 00:41:20.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He did. Look.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:41:24.494 --> 00:41:25.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is confusing.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:41:27.294 --> 00:41:31.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last time I read this poem,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it ended after the 12th stanza.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:41:31.813 --> 00:41:33.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the timeline's been changed,</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:41:34.532 --> 00:41:36.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>then why do I remember things</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the way they used to be?</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:41:37.210 --> 00:41:39.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets work in mysterious ways.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:41:42.169 --> 00:41:42.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: Excuse me, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:41:43.488 --> 00:41:44.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:41:44.529 --> 00:41:48.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sorry to bother you, but tomorrow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after evening services in the Temple,</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:41:48.887 --> 00:41:51.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we're having my daughter's</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i></i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>ih'tanu </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>ceremony.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:41:52.966 --> 00:41:54.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's turning 14.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:41:54.885 --> 00:41:55.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Happy birthday.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:41:57.165 --> 00:42:00.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were wondering if there's any chance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you could come and give her your blessing.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:42:01.564 --> 00:42:02.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It would mean so much to us.</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:42:03.642 --> 00:42:04.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd be happy to.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:42:06.722 --> 00:42:07.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:42:08.881 --> 00:42:09.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're welcome.</c.bg_transparent>

